msgid ""
"Discover, install, and update your applications effortlessly. Kiosque "
"provides a modern, fast experience for managing your Flatpaks, inspired by "
"Flathub."
msgstr ""
"Découvrez, installez et mettez à jour vos applications sans effort. Kiosque "
"offre une expérience moderne et rapide pour gérer vos Flatpaks, inspirée de "
"Flathub."

